{"tid":2413038,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢家個安心出行根本未變完全體","createTime":"2021-02-18T11:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T11:58:45.000Z","uid":113951,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7b60a5a0345d9414e23d87cac2fa6c297e5238","tid":2413038,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:31:20.000Z","msg":"大把DLC可以加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//純粹從學術上探討，以今天「安心出行」的設計，比較起TT，似乎本地差佬就只能心中羨慕。<br />\n<br />\n  因為如果要存取「安心出行」的到訪資料，「理論上」確實不如新加坡般方便：先要強行存取到用家本機的紀錄，方可破解出追蹤紀錄(之前專文分析過技術上並不困難)。但當然一旦&rdquo;hack&rdquo;到，本港法庭有權接受非法取得證據，故此一樣可以「依法」呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n 「安心出行」2.0可全面更改架構變新加坡模式<br />\n<br />\n故此如果參考新加坡政府整套推行TT的方法，顯示在這一邊，「安心出行」是大有收窄私隱的空間。例如可以強制實名登記、還有強制部份「疫區」和指定「高風險」人士使用等等。<br />\n<br />\n  甚至當人人都習慣日常生活中使用之後，索性推出「安心出行」2.0，全面改以中央上載資料方式管理到訪地點數據。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/602afcf0da97cc6a75566eb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F602afcf0da97cc6a75566eb2&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69A2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=23e67093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/602afcf0da97cc6a75566eb2</a><br />\n<br />\n其他公開研究緊既功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6029c790827875169eab8f5e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F6029c790827875169eab8f5e&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69A2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=cbac3fac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/6029c790827875169eab8f5e</a>"},{"pid":"32a3f119c3c47bf3823ce35fc5d162347d3a3e0d","tid":2413038,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a